Title: Vietnamnese and Australian Wedding
DateModified: '2019-02-16'
DatePublished: '2019-02-16'
Url: https://www.worldnomads.com/create/scholarships/writing/2019/applications/vietnamnese-and-australian-wedding
SetInCountry: Vietnam
Category: Making a local connection
AuthorName: Monalisa Nggilu
AuthorCountry: Indonesia
Text: I went to Vietnam last months for my boyfriend friend wedding. And the wedding
  with the vietnamnese culture, i just knew it if traditional wedding in Vietnam its
  was so fancy, and the bridegroom must give some money to the bride's family, jewelry,
  and etc. But the bride's family was gave some jewelry also to the bride. The bride's
  gave some price money from family from the older uncle/aunt, sister, brother, and
  friends. For the wedding it was finished within 2 hours. But it was so great i can
  joined with this wedding.
